name: eDEAL Tickets
overview:
eDEAL Tickets is an Austin-based online marketing company designed to help busy and fun loving people discover local area businesses. Local area businesses are the charms of what makes the city vibrant, robust, and comfortable to live. eDEAL Tickets strives to promote each business by attracting new customers and building customer loyalty to make local area businesses an integral part of a city people desire to live.

eDEAL Tickets features incredible daily deals to local area businesses. They are kicking things off in Texas and covering the major cities including: Austin, Dallas, Ft. Worth, Houston, and San Antonio.
